.TH LIGHTNING-CHANNEL-AGE-SKEWNESS 1
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-age-skewness \- compute skewness of channel age distribution in days
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning channel-age-skewness
.SH DESCRIPTION
Queries listpeerchannels and computes the skewness of the channel age distribution in days.
.SH OUTPUT
JSON object with field \fBage_skewness_days\fR.
